episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Introduction
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku Developer Relations team welcomes Roku developers to the 2020 Developer Summit.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku Developer Relations team welcomes Roku developers to the 2020 Developer Summit.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Welcome address
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku content team reviews Roku's accomplishments in 2020 and discusses the ongoing evolution and trends in streaming.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku content team reviews Roku's accomplishments in 2020 and discusses the ongoing evolution and trends in streaming.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Fall updates: Hardware & OS
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku Product team discusses the updated hardware lineup and new Roku OS features for Fall 2020.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku Product team discusses the updated hardware lineup and new Roku OS features for Fall 2020.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Developer updates
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku Partner Management team presents the latest updates to SceneGraph and BrightScript APIs and new features in the Developer Dashboard.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku Partner Management team presents the latest updates to SceneGraph and BrightScript APIs and new features in the Developer Dashboard.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Certification update
episodes.shortDescription: The Partner Management team discusses the latest updates made to the Roku channel certification criteria for Fall 2020.
episodes.longDescription: The Partner Management team discusses the latest updates made to the Roku channel certification criteria for Fall 2020.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Roku Pay
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku Pay team describes the latest updates to Roku's payment platform.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku Pay team describes the latest updates to Roku's payment platform.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Demand API
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku advertising team discusses how the Demand API helps publishers monetize video ad inventory more efficiently.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku advertising team discusses how the Demand API helps publishers monetize video ad inventory more efficiently.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Growing an audience
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku Partner Growth Management team explains how to maximize reach, engagement, and revenue through the lifecycle of a channel. The team also hosts a panel with some of the top streaming services discussing their success with building and monetizing audiences on the Roku platform.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku Partner Growth Management team explains how to maximize reach, engagement, and revenue through the lifecycle of a channel. The team also hosts a panel with some of the top streaming services discussing their success with building and monetizing audiences on the Roku platform.

episodes.title: Roku 2020 Developer Summit: Panel discussion
episodes.shortDescription: The Roku Developer Relations team moderates a panel discussion with Roku engineers, who answer live questions fron the Roku developer community.
episodes.longDescription: The Roku Developer Relations team moderates a panel discussion with Roku engineers, who answer live questions fron the Roku developer community.
